Now, we can sum the distances: 
Total distance = 1 (bygger-ofte) + 2 (bygger-på) + 3 (bygger-att) + 1 (linselement-ett) + 4 (bygger-linselement) + 1 (linselement-i) + 1 (i-objektivet) + 3 (linselement-eller) + 1 (eller-att) + 1 (bildsensorn-hela) + 3 (eller-bildsensorn) + 1 (kan-förflyttas) + 5 (att-förflyttas) + 1 (förflyttas-i) + 2 (plan-sina) + 1 (plan-respektive) + 1 (i-plan)
Total distance = 36

The number of dependencies in the sentence is 18.

Average dependency distance = Total distance / Number of dependencies 
Average dependency distance = 36 / 18 ≈ 2.